 <title>Test Domain</title>
  <para>The test domain is a domain for all test tools, like <link xlink:href="http://maven.apache.org/">Maven</link>.</para> 
  <section>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>The test domain runs all tests for a specific pre-configured project or suite of projects.</para>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>Functional Interface</title>
    <para><link xlink:href="${github.base}openengsb-domain-test${github.master.path}src/main/java/org/openengsb/domain/test/TestDomain.java">Link</link>
      to the Java Domain Interface on Github.  This interface also contains information about events raised by this domain.</para>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>Connectors</title>  
    This domain is implemented by the <xref linkend="domains.multiple.maven" />, which supports multiple domains.
  </section>

</chapter>
